snippet.textDisplay:
The only way to win that battle is to never yield. Do good for the kid, turn the other cheek, and in doing so, assert dominance and heap burning coals. It's just pain. Also, you could totally setup a bunch of cameras to catch'em in the act, etc. Get him agrivated, lure him out. Just tell the mom the truth, don't give in. You'll build trust with her, then she'll see you have no reason to be lying. Then, only two things can happen - the kid gives up, or you die trying.

Victory, or an honorable death. You only lose if you give in.

Maybe she'll get tired of hearing it and break it off. That's on her, her loss. Surround yourself with success, better environments, and later you can say, "look at me - I have nothing to lose and nothing to gain in saying this: I was telling the truth". They'll eventually question their doubts, no doubt.
